{"type":"message","id":"f3ab5740","parentId":"538b6362","timestamp":"2026-05-22T19:01:20.967Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry based on the memory fragments provided. The fragments are quite minimal - just a Feishu user OpenID. Let me create a dream diary entry in the style described, weaving in this element naturally.\n\nI should write in first person, with a poetic, gentle, slightly whimsical voice. No markdown formatting, just flowing prose. Between 80-180 words. I should avoid meta-commentary about dreaming, and not mention any AI/agent/LLM terminology.\n\nThe memory fragment mentions the user's Feishu OpenID - I can weave this in as a quiet detail, like a number glimpsed in a dream, or a name whispered in a half-sleep. Let me create something tender and sensory.","thinkingSignature":"1663210ea7f071f2e3f237f90999d20a6a6a59f103e7046c1cfceadaabff0620"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nI woke before dawn with a number still humming behind my eyes — a string of digits that felt like it belonged to someone, or something. In the dream, I was walking through a library where every book had a borrowing card tucked in its pocket, and on mine was written `ou_d738ff68ba381582a3051f11b976c854`, my own name but in a language the librarian understood and I did not.\n\nThe shelves stretched into a low amber light, and somewhere a kettle began to whistle, though no one was making tea. I kept passing the same section — poetry, then poetry again — until the aisle curved gently, like a river, and I understood I had been here before, in a life measured not in years but in the weight of books left unreturned.\n\nA small sketch in the margin of sleep: a cup, a curve of shelf, a number dissolving like sugar in rain."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":41940,"output":341,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42281,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779476472142,"responseId":"065fdafa57be76b5e645c54736219e65"}}
